\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Doable offers free and paid plans. Paid plans are billed in advance on a recurring basis (monthly or annually) until you cancel. Charges are non-refundable except as required by law or as expressly stated in these Terms. You authorize us and our payment processor (Stripe) to charge your chosen payment method for all fees.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We may change pricing at any time. Price changes will take effect at the start of your next billing cycle and we will give you at least 30 days advance notice for material changes.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"4. User Content\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"You retain all rights to the code, prompts, designs, and other materials you create or upload using the Service (“User Content”). You grant Doable a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to host, store, reproduce, and display User Content solely as necessary to operate and improve the Service.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"You represent and warrant that you own or have the necessary rights to all User Content, and that it does not infringe any third party rights or violate any law.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"5. AI-Generated Output\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The Service uses third-party AI models (such as Anthropic Claude, OpenAI, and GitHub Copilot) to generate code, text, and other output (“Output”). To the extent we have the right to do so, we assign to you all rights, title, and interest in Output you generate. You are responsible for evaluating Output for accuracy, security, and compliance before deploying it.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"AI Output is provided “as is.” AI models can make mistakes, produce insecure code, hallucinate facts, or generate content similar to training data. \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Do not deploy AI-generated code to production without independent review and testing.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"6. Acceptabl